---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Franconia Family Dental"
  description="Terms of Service for Franconia Family Dental. Please read these terms carefully before using our services."
>
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-sky-700" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-600 mb-12">Last updated: January 1, 2025</p>

      <div class="space-y-10 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">

        <section aria-labelledby="agreement-heading">
          <h2 id="agreement-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing our website or becoming a patient at Franconia Family Dental, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.</p>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="appointments-heading">
          <h2 id="appointments-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Appointments & Cancellations</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4 text-slate-600">
            <li>We ask for at least 24 hours notice to cancel or reschedule appointments</li>
            <li>Repeated late cancellations or no-shows may result in a cancellation fee</li>
            <li>We will make every effort to accommodate emergency dental needs</li>
            <li>Appointment times are reserved specifically for you — please arrive on time</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="payment-heading">
          <h2 id="payment-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Payment & Insurance</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4 text-slate-600">
            <li>Payment is due at the time of service unless other arrangements have been made</li>
            <li>We accept most major insurance plans — please verify coverage before your appointment</li>
            <li>You are responsible for any amounts not covered by your insurance</li>
            <li>We accept cash, check, and major credit cards</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="website-heading">
          <h2 id="website-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Website Use</h2>
          <p>The information on this website is provided for general informational purposes only and does not constitute professional dental advice. Always consult with a qualified dental professional for advice specific to your situation.</p>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="liability-heading">
          <h2 id="liability-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Franconia Family Dental shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of our website or services. Our liability is limited to the fullest extent permitted by applicable law.</p>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="changes-heading">
          <h2 id="changes-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Patients will be notified of significant changes. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section aria-labelledby="contact-heading">
          <h2 id="contact-heading" class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:</p>
          <address class="not-italic mt-4 text-slate-600">
            Franconia Family Dental<br />
            123 Main Street<br />
            Franconia, NH 03580<br />
            <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="text-sky-700 hover:text-sky-800 hover:underline focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 rounded">(555) 123-4567</a><br />
            <a href="mailto:info@franconiafamilydental.com" class="text-sky-700 hover:text-sky-800 hover:underline focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-sky-500 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 rounded">info@franconiafamilydental.com</a>
          </address>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>